{"tid":1263352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1行動與和理非和樂合作版","createTime":"2019-06-28T06:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T11:57:17.000Z","uid":172733,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"67b4ca3fed30a8d770da7b9ac8fa919a1f312636","tid":1263352,"uid":172733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"香港扯旗日<br />\n行動與和理非和樂升旗日， 前線升旗， 和理非唱歌阻黑警捉人<br />\n<br />\n用咩旗：純黑旗<br />\n要十張八張<br />\n<br />\nPlan A［室外升旗］<br />\n早上搶旗桿/旗桿附近掛自制黑旗， 其他人可以自備黑旗fing , 將黑旗掛到成個港島都係( 燈柱etc)<br />\n<br />\nPlan B ［港共決定室內升旗］<br />\n唔理佢地， 照做plan A<br />\n<br />\n以上所有plan！！！！：<br />\n觀眾位：fing長棍大旗，其餘手持細旗仔，及大聲唱英文版do you hear the people sing，蓋國歌聲。勇士則自行決定，安全為上。和理非中意做咩就做咩， 唔好跑唔好阻人衝唔好捉鬼<br />\n完曬有多大旗就遍地開花，周圍升，有杆就升/ fing長棍大旗遊走<br />\n<br />\n630可留守廣場，驚佢封路，所以要提早入場，然後退返去觀眾位<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Wearehkersss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWearehkersss&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=56481e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Wearehkersss</a>"},{"pid":"ae5a1e06919bc0ca7d28cfe927c5fa5f8aaa6baf","tid":1263352,"uid":180462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e478de2feae74b724b250d7414f2a31d76aa2180","tid":1263352,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b5e49359ec9733ae075f8258a7db6ed74fe711","tid":1263352,"uid":73297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2093dbba02048fc7d9ba37b01f2ea1905542329","tid":1263352,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,